title: [Black Moor, Wastelands]
description: A sea of swirling grey mist covers the buckled, dark ground, seeping up from irregular crevices in the landscape to swirl in the constant whistling wind.  A few slabs of ancient stone lie scattered about the moor, pitted by centuries of moisture and stained with patches of black and grey lichen.
